{"data":[{"date":"00:36 20/08","title":"Mourinho: \u201cMartial ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec Sanchez ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/mourinho-martial-chi-duoc-thi-dau-vi-sanchez-chan-thuong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a HLV B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha khi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfn Brighton.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cAlexis \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd s\u1ebd \u0111i c\u00f9ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nh\u1ecf v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng, ch\u00ednh th\u1ebf m\u00e0 t\u00f4i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0 trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c.\u201d \u2013 HLV Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Brighton vs MU.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Brighton vs MU v\u1ec1 Martial h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Brighton vs MU v\u1ec1 Martial h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/23.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Brighton vs MU v\u1ec1 Martial</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Sanchez nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Marcus Rashford hay Jesse Lingard, ch\u00ednh Anthony Martial m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh thay th\u1ebf, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. Mourinho ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Anthony b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ee7 hi\u1ec3u c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang t\u1eebng ng\u00e0y gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Jesse m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eb9, th\u1ebf n\u00ean c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cMarcus c\u00f3 v\u1ebb l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean h\u01a1n cho h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ai \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0m ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng cho Lukaku b\u1edfi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 90 ph\u00fat. N\u1ebfu xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t c\u1ea3 hai th\u00ec sau \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t ai \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Martial \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 n\u00e9m \u0111i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec c\u1ea3 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 Man Utd c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-3 trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch xu\u1ed1ng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Video tr\u1eadn Brighton 3-2 MU:<br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279543\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/20/brighton-manutd.mp4&autoplay=false&mute=false&vtype=1&playType=0&_admParamTvc=0;0;0;0&_listsuggest=https://kenh14s.cnnd.vn/Handler/Video/ListVideoXML.ashx?watch=0&postroll=true&replay=true&nonVol=true&volume=0.6&boxVideoID=ifVideo-0&nopre=true&midroll=0.8;20s&urlParent=http://kenh14.vn/truc-tiep-h2-brighton-3-2-man-utd-pogba-ghi-ban-tren-cham-phat-den-20180819142040755.chn\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2555","checkdouble":"194846"},{"date":"00:48 20/08","title":"B\u00e1o ch\u00ed qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/bao-chi-quoc-te-noi-gi-khi-olympic-viet-nam-da-bai-nhat-ban.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018. V\u00e0 b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y?</h2><h2>B\u00e1o ch\u00ed qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi\u00a0Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi Malaysia b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng E h\u00f4m 17/8 v\u1eeba qua, t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi \u2018h\u1ea1 \u0111o v\u00e1n\u2019 m\u1ed9t n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c l\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng D di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u 19/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1edbm c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc ngay \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u1edd c\u00e1i ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i r\u1ea5t \u2018ngoan\u2019 c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i. Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 mong manh \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u00e1o ch\u00ed qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u00e1o ch\u00ed qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/ku9ggb39kijb6lpobmym.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf h\u1ebft\u00a0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c 1-0, \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Park Hang Seo. V\u00e0 gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, trang ch\u1ee7 L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 (AFC) \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ca ng\u1ee3i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 k\u00edn k\u1ebd c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, AFC c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, t\u1edd Tokyo Sports c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt l\u1ea1i cho r\u1eb1ng BHL Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh, \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Moriyasu Hajime l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ch\u1ebf \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 kho\u00e9t s\u00e2u v\u00e0o \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00ean \u0111\u00e0nh ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng D.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd b\u00e1o Th\u00e1i Lan Siam Sport l\u1ea1i khen ng\u1ee3i tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Trang b\u00e1o n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 non n\u1edbt kinh nghi\u1ec7m tr\u1eadn m\u1ea1c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do ch\u00ednh khi\u1ebfn Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c hay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, t\u1edd Goal phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Indonesia l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018. Ngo\u00e0i ra, t\u1edd b\u00e1o n\u00e0y c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng Quang H\u1ea3i ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng khi gi\u00fap\u00a0Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00ecn chung gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u khi m\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1. Ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D gi\u00fap Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ea1ng 3 \u1edf 1 trong 3 b\u1ea3ng B/E/F s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh sau lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai 20/8.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-dau-han-quoc-va-nhung-kich-ban-thu-vi-cho-olympic-viet-nam-tai-vong-18-asiad-168-194840.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/doi-dau-han-quoc-va-nhung-kich-ban-thu-vi-cho-olympic-viet-nam-tai-vong-18-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-dau-han-quoc-va-nhung-kich-ban-thu-vi-cho-olympic-viet-nam-tai-vong-18-asiad-168-194840.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n th\u00fa v\u1ecb cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 ASIAD</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 n\u1eb1m trong c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng B/E/F. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n th\u00fa v\u1ecb n\u00e0o...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-duoc-thuong-nong-sau-chien-thang-truoc-nhat-ban-168-194843.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/olympic-viet-nam-duoc-thuong-nong-sau-chien-thang-truoc-nhat-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-duoc-thuong-nong-sau-chien-thang-truoc-nhat-ban-168-194843.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00f3ng sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\n\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t ngay sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-bat-ngo-khen-mot-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194841.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-bat-ngo-khen-mot-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-bat-ngo-khen-mot-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194841.html\">HLV Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khen m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nSau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2554","checkdouble":"194847"},{"date":"01:16 20/08","title":"C\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 MU b\u1ecb b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i t\u1ed5ng s\u1ec9 v\u1ea3 sau th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i \u1edf Brighton","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/cap-trung-ve-mu-bi-bo-doi-huyen-thoai-tong-si-va-sau-tham-bai-o-brighton.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t trong tr\u1eadn thua 2-3 c\u1ee7a M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span id=\"ctl00_m_contentBody_sp_title\" class=\"sp_title\" style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: start;\">Pogba l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng xin l\u1ed7i sau tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a M.U</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: start;\">&nbsp;<br>\r\n</span><br style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: start;\">\r\nTrong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 2018/19, CLB Man United \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i mu\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng y\u1ebfu Brighton &amp; Hove Albion.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Glenn Murray, Shane Duffy v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Pascal Gross&nbsp;\u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Brighton gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf Man Utd. Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pogba \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba\" title=\"Pogba\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/pogba-len-tieng-xin-loi-sau-tran-thua-bac-nhuoc-cua-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Pogba th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t trong tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thua, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. H\u00f4m nay c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brighton \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0 h\u1ecd x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00f4m nay, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e1i t\u00f4i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00ean tr\u00ean. Th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p. N\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn M.U li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp m\u1eafc nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i&rdquo;, Pogba n\u00f3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pogba c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 M.U s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 x\u1ea3y ra trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Mourinho c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn M.U x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cho nh\u1eefng sai s\u00f3t \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Brighton. &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ed7i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00f4m nay, v\u00e0 Brighton \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t ch\u00fang t\u00f4i trong m\u1ecdi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng. M.U \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 khi thi\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, b\u1ea1n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n m\u1ea5t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u01b0\u1edbng&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, sau 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, M.U x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 10 v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 3, Pogba v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Tottenham Hotspur v\u00e0o 02h00 ng\u00e0y 28/08 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>Highlight: Brighton 2-0 MU (V\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19)<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></em><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279543\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/08/20/brighton-manutd.mp4&amp;autoplay=false&amp;mute=false&amp;vtype=1&amp;playType=0&amp;_admParamTvc=0;0;0;0&amp;_listsuggest=https://kenh14s.cnnd.vn/Handler/Video/ListVideoXML.ashx?watch=0&amp;postroll=true&amp;replay=true&amp;nonVol=true&amp;volume=0.6&amp;boxVideoID=ifVideo-0&amp;nopre=true&amp;midroll=0.8;20s&amp;urlParent=http://kenh14.vn/truc-tiep-h2-brighton-3-2-man-utd-pogba-ghi-ban-tren-cham-phat-den-20180819142040755.chn\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msa