th\u1ea3m \u1edf Brighton","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/mourinho-cay-dang-chia-se-ve-tran-thua-tham-o-brighton.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Man Utd c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng ra v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi hai b\u00e0n tay tr\u1eafng sau m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 k\u00e9m c\u1ecfi ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i chi\u1ec1u th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Man Utd khi v\u1edbi sai l\u1ea7m n\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfp sai l\u1ea7m, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trung b\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 Brighton li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn ba l\u1ea7n ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 45 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a hai ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t Paul Pogba v\u00e0 Romelu Lukaku ch\u1ec9 t\u1ef1a nh\u01b0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c g\u1ee1 g\u1ea1c ch\u00fat \u00edt danh d\u1ef1 cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf. Tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jose Mourinho t\u1ee5t xu\u1ed1ng ng\u1ee5p l\u1eb7n \u1edf n\u1eeda gi\u1eefa b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng Premier League 2018/19.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Brighton vs MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Brighton vs MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/mourinho-cay-dang-chia-se-ve-tran-thua-tham-o-brighton.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Brighton vs MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">HLV Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Brighton vs MU v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 cay \u0111\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 thua 2-3: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u sai l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t. \u0110\u00f4i khi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 may m\u1eafn tho\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1eadu qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u00f4m nay th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf, c\u1ee9 m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i l\u00e0 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh trong gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 hi\u1ec7p hai, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i c\u1ee9 nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 Brighton c\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i c\u00e0ng hay v\u00e0 h\u00fat h\u1ebft s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eady. Do \u0111\u00f3 m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0 ph\u00e1 s\u1ea3n k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ec7n, th\u1ebf r\u1ed3i hy v\u1ecdng k\u1ebft th\u00fac hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thua 1-2 c\u0169ng tan t\u00e0nh m\u00e2y kh\u00f3i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 suy s\u1ee5p tinh th\u1ea7n. M\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn qu\u00e1 mu\u1ed9n m\u00e0ng, trong khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ef1c ch\u1edd mau ch\u00f3ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o h\u1ebft.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Man Utd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t ch\u00fat n\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Tottenham \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n sau tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Old Trafford.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h2><strong>Video tr\u1eadn Brighton 3-2 MU:<br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279543\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/20/brighton-manutd.mp4&autoplay=false&mute=false&vtype=1&playType=0&_admParamTvc=0;0;0;0&_listsuggest=https://kenh14s.cnnd.vn/Handler/Video/ListVideoXML.ashx?watch=0&postroll=true&replay=true&nonVol=true&volume=0.6&boxVideoID=ifVideo-0&nopre=true&midroll=0.8;20s&urlParent=http://kenh14.vn/truc-tiep-h2-brighton-3-2-man-utd-pogba-ghi-ban-tren-cham-phat-den-20180819142040755.chn\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-vs-man-city-172-194853.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/mourinho-cay-dang-chia-se-ve-tran-thua-tham-o-brighton.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-vs-man-city-172-194853.html\">Man Utd thua nh\u1ee5c: \u0110\u00fang r\u1ed3i Jose, ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p!</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton cho th\u1ea5y Jose Mourinho gi\u1edd \u1edf v\u1ecb th\u1ebf m\u00e0 l\u1eddi m\u1ec9a mai Man City nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho Pep Guardiola ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p n\u1eefa r\u1ed3i,...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2552","checkdouble":"194849"},{"date":"06:15 20/08","title":"Guardiola \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd Mourinho: \"Man City kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/guardiola-dong-y-mourinho-man-city-khong-the-mua-dang-cap.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch m\u1ec9a mai c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 v\u1ec1 b\u1ed9 phim t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chuy\u1ec7n l\u00e0 Manchester City m\u1edbi ra m\u1eaft m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 phim t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u ghi l\u1ea1i h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch tranh th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3u h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m Man Utd, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi tr\u00edch \u0111o\u1ea1n m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn derby Manchester l\u00e0 \u201ct\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 d\u1ef1ng xe bus\u201d.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pep Guardiola n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Jose Mourinho, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Pep Guardiola n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Jose Mourinho, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/guardiola-dong-y-mourinho-man-city-khong-the-mua-dang-cap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pep Guardiola n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Jose Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\">Hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean HLV Jose Mourinho b\u00ean kia th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u00e0 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf c\u00f4ng khai: \u201cAnh v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m phim hay m\u00e0 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c, trong khi t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 trong b\u1ed9 phim \u1ea5y. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng ti\u1ec1n b\u1ea1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady th\u00ec t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Pep Guardiola, \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 gay g\u1eaft \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch m\u1ec9a mai c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p x\u1ee9 B\u1ed3, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh quan \u0111i\u1ec3m. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng Man City 6-1 Huddersfield:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\">\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi Jose r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thi\u1ebfu t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Man Utd. \u0110\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee7 \u00fd c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i khi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi l\u1ea1i trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ra s\u1ef1 vi\u1ec7c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0m phim \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c C\u0110V hi\u1ec3u h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1ec9a x\u00f3i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean r\u1ed3i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u00fd ki\u1ebfn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Jose m\u00e0.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\">M\u00e0n h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Huddersfield t\u1ea1m \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Man City l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng Premier League 2018/19 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Liverpool ra qu\u00e2n \u0111\u00eam nay. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-khinh-bi-man-city-va-doi-tien-catxe-dong-phim-172-194838.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/mourinho-khinh-bi-man-city-va-doi-tien-catxe-dong-phim.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-khinh-bi-man-city-va-doi-tien-catxe-dong-phim-172-194838.html\">Mourinho khinh b\u1ec9 Man City v\u00e0... \u0111\u00f2i ti\u1ec1n c\u00e1t-x\u00ea \u0111\u00f3ng phim</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-vs-man-city-172-194853.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/mourinho-cay-dang-chia-se-ve-tran-thua-tham-o-brighton.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-vs-man-city-172-194853.html\">Man Utd thua nh\u1ee5c: \u0110\u00fang r\u1ed3i Jose, ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p!</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton cho th\u1ea5y Jose Mourinho gi\u1edd \u1edf v\u1ecb th\u1ebf m\u00e0 l\u1eddi m\u1ec9a mai Man City nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho Pep Guardiola ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p n\u1eefa r\u1ed3i,...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2551","checkdouble":"194850"},{"date":"03:59 20/08","title":"Pogba l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng xin l\u1ed7i sau tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/pogba-len-tieng-xin-loi-sau-tran-thua-bac-nhuoc-cua-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t trong tr\u1eadn thua 2-3 c\u1ee7a M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span id=\"ctl00_m_contentBody_sp_title\" class=\"sp_title\" style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: start;\">Pogba l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng xin l\u1ed7i sau tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a M.U</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: start;\">&nbsp;<br>\r\n</span><br style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: start;\">\r\nTrong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 2018/19, CLB Man United \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i mu\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng y\u1ebfu Brighton &amp; Hove Albion.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Glenn Murray, Shane Duffy v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Pascal Gross&nbsp;\u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Brighton gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf Man Utd. Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pogba \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba\" title=\"Pogba\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/pogba-len-tieng-xin-loi-sau-tran-thua-bac-nhuoc-cua-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Pogba th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t trong tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thua, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. H\u00f4m nay c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brighton \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0 h\u1ecd x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00f4m nay, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e1i t\u00f4i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00ean tr\u00ean. Th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p. N\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn M.U li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp m\u1eafc nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i&rdquo;, Pogba n\u00f3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pogba c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 M.U s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 x\u1ea3y ra trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Mourinho c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn M.U x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cho nh\u1eefng sai s\u00f3t \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Brighton. &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ed7i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00f4m nay, v\u00e0 Brighton \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t ch\u00fang t\u00f4i trong m\u1ecdi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng. M.U \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 khi thi\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, b\u1ea1n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n m\u1ea5t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u01b0\u1edbng&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, sau 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, M.U x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 10 v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 3, Pogba v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Tottenham Hotspur v\u00e0o 02h00 ng\u00e0y 28/08 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>Highlight: Brighton 2-0 MU (V\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19)<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></em><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279543\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/08/20/brighton-manutd.mp4&amp;autoplay=false&amp;mute=false&amp;vtype=1&amp;playType=0&amp;_admParamTvc=0;0;0;0&amp;_listsuggest=https://kenh14s.cnnd.vn/Handler/Video/ListVideoXML.ashx?watch=0&amp;postroll=true&amp;replay=true&amp;nonVol=true&amp;volume=0.6&amp;boxVideoID=ifVideo-0&amp;nopre=true&amp;midroll=0.8;20s&amp;urlParent=http://kenh14.vn/truc-tiep-h2-brighton-3-2-man-utd-pogba-ghi-ban-tren-cham-phat-den-20180819142040755.chn\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-martial-chi-duoc-thi-dau-vi-sanchez-chan-thuong-172-194846.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/mourinho-martial-chi-duoc-thi-dau-vi-sanchez-chan-thuong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-martial-chi-duoc-thi-dau-vi-sanchez-chan-thuong-172-194846.html\">Mourinho: &ldquo;Martial ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec Sanchez ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nL\u00fd gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a HLV B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha khi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfn Brighton.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cap-trung-ve-mu-bi-bo-doi-huyen-thoai-tong-si-va-sau-tham-bai-o-brighton-172-194848.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/cap-trung-ve-mu-bi-bo-doi-huyen-thoai-tong-si-va-sau-tham-bai-o-brighton.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cap-trung-ve-mu-bi-bo-doi-huyen-thoai-tong-si-va-sau-tham-bai-o-brighton-172-194848.html\">C\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 MU b\u1ecb b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i t\u1ed5ng s\u1ec9 v\u1ea3 sau th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i \u1edf Brighton</span><br>\r\nEric Bailly v\u00e0 Victor Lindelof tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a Gary Neville v\u00e0 Paul Scholes sau tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2550","checkdouble":"194851"},{"date":"04:41 20/08","title":"M.U thua tan n\u00e1t, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Scholes n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/scholes-noi-ve-that-bai-cua-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 M.U thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng y\u1ebfu Brighton & Hove Albion ngay \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Scholes \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.\r\n\r\n</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span id=\"ctl00_m_contentBody_sp_title\" class=\"sp_title\" style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; font-family: arial, verdana, \" lucida=\"\">Scholes n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a M.U</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, \" lucida=\"\">\u00a0</span><br style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, \" lucida=\"\">\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa M.U v\u00e0 Brighton di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ed1i 19/8, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y sau khi tr\u1ea3i qua 90 ph\u00fat \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng Amex c\u1ee7a Brighton.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng M.U \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft, trong khi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Victor Lindelof - Eric Bailly. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i mu\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thu\u1ed9c t\u1ed1p d\u01b0\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Scholes n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a MU  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Scholes n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a MU  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/scholes-noi-ve-that-bai-cua-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"width: 779px;\">\r\n            <table style=\"text-align: center; width: 777px;\">\r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td><em>M.U c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton<br>\r\n                        </em></td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 Jose Mourinho \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p cho M.U, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Paul Scholes \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i r\u1ed3i m\u00e0. M.U s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 M.U th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 khi nh\u00ecn c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch Bailly nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Scholes c\u0169ng n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng trung v\u1ec7 Victor Lindelof\u00a0kh\u00f4ng theo k\u00e8m Murray v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Brighton.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Lindelof \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1m trong vi\u1ec7c ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a M.U. \u0110\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ra khi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1t v\u00e0o trong, anh \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n nhanh nh\u1eb9n h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng ra thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1eaft vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3. N\u00f3 th\u1eadt \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng M.U c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng t\u1edbi c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ea1nh tranh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Sau tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ee5t xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 10 tr\u00ean BXH. V\u00e0 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Tottenham \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 3 NHA v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pogba-len-tieng-xin-loi-sau-tran-thua-bac-nhuoc-cua-mu-172-194851.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/pogba-len-tieng-xin-loi-sau-tran-thua-bac-nhuoc-cua-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pogba-len-tieng-xin-loi-sau-tran-thua-bac-nhuoc-cua-mu-172-194851.html\">Pogba l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng xin l\u1ed7i sau tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a M.U</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t trong tr\u1eadn thua 2-3 c\u1ee7a M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cap-trung-ve-mu-bi-bo-doi-huyen-thoai-tong-si-va-sau-tham-bai-o-brighton-172-194848.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/cap-trung-ve-mu-bi-bo-doi-huyen-thoai-tong-si-va-sau-tham-bai-o-brighton.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cap-trung-ve-mu-bi-bo-doi-huyen-thoai-tong-si-va-sau-tham-bai-o-brighton-172-194848.html\">C\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 MU b\u1ecb b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i t\u1ed5ng s\u1ec9 v\u1ea3 sau th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i \u1edf Brighton</span><br>\r\nEric Bailly v\u00e0 Victor Lindelof tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a Gary Neville v\u00e0 Paul Scholes sau tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</span></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2549","checkdouble":"194852"},{"date":"06:15 20/08","title":"Man Utd thua nh\u1ee5c: \u0110\u00fang r\u1ed3i Jose, ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/mourinho-cay-dang-chia-se-ve-tran-thua-tham-o-brighton.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton cho th\u1ea5y Jose Mourinho gi\u1edd \u1edf v\u1ecb th\u1ebf m\u00e0 l\u1eddi m\u1ec9a mai Man City nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho Pep Guardiola ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p n\u1eefa r\u1ed3i, v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u1ec9nh cao v\u00e0 m\u1eabu m\u1ef1c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00f3 \u00edt gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 n\u00f3i l\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. Chi b\u1eb1ng t\u1eadp trung chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n cho m\u00ecnh thay v\u00ec x\u1ec9a x\u00f3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng hay h\u01a1n sao?</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Jose Mourinho th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n ch\u1eb3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi \u00fd ki\u1ebfn v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed1n phim t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u \u201cT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec c\u1ea3\u201d c\u1ee7a Manchester City. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng ngh\u0129 sao v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Kevin Bruyne. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u00f4ng th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu n\u1ed5i v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng l\u1eafm r\u1ed3i.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<table cellpacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"padding:10px 0px;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\" width=\"44px\"><img src=\"/content/images/s1.png\" alt=\"comment left\" width=\"44px\"></td>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding: 10px; text-align: justify;\"><em>T\u00f4i \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi kh\u00e1c c\u01a1. C\u00e1c anh kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 b\u1ed9 phim \u0111\u00f3 sao? T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem n\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u. T\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t CLB gi\u00e0u c\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, ch\u1ee9 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1.</em></td>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\" width=\"44px\"><img src=\"/content/images/s2.png\" alt=\"comment right\" width=\"44px\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brighton vs MU \u0110\u00fang r\u1ed3i Jose, ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brighton vs MU \u0110\u00fang r\u1ed3i Jose, ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/Du-am-Brighton-vs-MU-Dung-roi-Jose,-tien-khong-the-mua-dang-cap-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brighton vs MU: Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf thua nh\u1ee5c trong chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n xu\u1ed1ng mi\u1ec1n bi\u1ec3n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng nam</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec7n th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 trong th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c 2-3 \u1edf Brighton, ch\u1ec9 \u00edt gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 sau khi Man City h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Huddersfield v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 6-1, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd v\u1ecb HLV c\u1ee7a Man Utd \u01b0\u1edbc sao m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i l\u1eafm v\u00e0 ngoa ngo\u1eaft \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Mourinho, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh v\u00ec sao h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c h\u01a1n tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 tr\u00ean c\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1ee7. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1ecb HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e1ng ra s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m h\u01a1n d\u00f9 \u00edt d\u00f9 nhi\u1ec1u, n\u1ebfu \u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n n\u01a1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, thay v\u00ec c\u1ee9 ph\u1ea3i \u0111i ch\u00fai m\u0169i sang x\u1ec9a x\u00f3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1eeb khu v\u1ef1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, Mourinho c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u00e9o m\u1eaft nh\u00ecn l\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i, c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ng\u1ed3i c\u1ee7a ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Ed Woodward v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea5p b\u1eadc l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Man Utd khi kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi cho \u00f4ng trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 Toby Alderweireld hay Harry Maguire.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00f4 l\u00fd n\u1ebfu h\u1ecfi ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1eaft \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 g\u00ec kh\u00e1 kh\u1ea9m h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 trong tay. Tr\u1edb tr\u00eau th\u1eadt khi d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 Eric Bailly v\u00e0 Victor Lindelof, hai b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1eb7c Bi\u1ec7t mang v\u1ec1 Old Trafford, ch\u1ec9 nh\u01b0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi mua th\u00eam m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bailly Lindelof\" title=\"Bailly Lindelof\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/cap-trung-ve-mu-bi-bo-doi-huyen-thoai-tong-si-va-sau-tham-bai-o-brighton.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brighton vs MU: Bu\u1ed5i chi\u1ec1u th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda c\u1ee7a c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 Bailly v\u00e0 Lindelof</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 th\u00ea th\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 MU trong chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n xu\u1ed1ng mi\u1ec1n bi\u1ec3n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng nam c\u00e0ng minh ch\u1ee9ng cho \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i tr\u1ebb trung v\u00e0 tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng sinh n\u0103m 1994 c\u1ee9 th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng Glenn Murray r\u1ed3i Pascal Gross k\u00e9m danh h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh h\u1ea1 n\u0103m l\u1ea7n b\u1ea3y l\u01b0\u1ee3t, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3 Fred, m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf, hai l\u1ea7n b\u1ecb c\u01b0\u1edbp b\u00f3ng d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Brighton.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Murray ch\u1ea1y b\u0103ng c\u1eaft qua m\u1eb7t Lindelof, g\u1ea9y b\u00f3ng nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng v\u00e0 tinh t\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i David De Gea v\u00e0 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. L\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0103ng ngang b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i theo h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, n\u01a1i Ashley Young b\u1ecb khai th\u00e1c v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u01b0a k\u1ecbp ho\u00e0n h\u1ed3n m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ea7n sau b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Bailly lu\u1ed1ng cu\u1ed1ng ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng \u0111i h\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng bi\u00ean ngang khi \u00e1p l\u1ef1c g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ee7 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 MU, khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft g\u1ecdn gh\u1ebd m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 2-3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m v\u1eady. Sau m\u1ed9t h\u1ed3i l\u1ed9n x\u1ed9n trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba, Shane Duffy c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac \u0111\u00fang ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau \u0111\u00f3, Romelu Lukaku l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u1eafp l\u1ea1i hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb d\u1eadp t\u1eaft kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ebfc c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau \u0111\u00f3. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ea9u th\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a De Gea \u0111\u1ea9y Fred v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3, Brighton gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t ngay khu trung l\u1ed9 v\u00e0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng. Bailly v\u00e0 Lindelof l\u01a1 ng\u01a1 thi\u1ebfu \u0103n \u00fd, \u0111\u1ec3 Gross \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 khu 16m50 nh\u01b0 ch\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb trung v\u1ec7 B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m 11m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Jose Mourinho phat bieu tran Brighton vs MU\" title=\"HLV Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Brighton vs MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/mourinho-cay-dang-chia-se-ve-tran-thua-tham-o-brighton.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brighton vs MU: Mourinho gi\u1edd th\u00ea th\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 Guardiola ch\u1ea5p v\u1eb7t l\u1eddi m\u1ec9a mai</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i chi\u1ec1u th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda c\u1ee7a Man Utd t\u1eeb kho\u1ea3n ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 l\u00ean tr\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, khi Brighton \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh c\u1ea3 hi\u1ec7p hai \u0111\u1ec3 co c\u1ee5m v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng trong ch\u00e2n. Kh\u00f4ng, ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Paul Pogba, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ch\u00ednh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ee1 g\u1ea1c l\u1ea1i ch\u00fat \u00edt danh d\u1ef1 trong th\u1eddi gian b\u00f9 gi\u1edd. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Anthony Martial t\u1ef1 v\u1ee9t \u0111i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n hi\u1ebfm hoi khi Alexis Sanchez b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e0ng t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea9y m\u00ecnh ra kh\u1ecfi Old Trafford, c\u00f2n Lukaku v\u00f4 h\u00ecnh m\u1ea5t d\u1ea1ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb World Cup 2018 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed9t Man Utd khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng trong ch\u00e2n m\u1edbi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Man Utd t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t, m\u1ec9a mai thay khi nh\u1edb ra r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 lu\u00f4n hay t\u1eebng l\u00e0 s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Mourinho. Nh\u1eefng lo ng\u1ea1i h\u1ed3i h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha tr\u1edf n\u00ean ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u01b0ng th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho \u00f4ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ec7n, vi\u1ec7c \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Mourinho t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng m\u1ecdi c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Man City trong ph\u00f2ng h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o, nh\u01b0ng minh ch\u1ee9ng tr\u1ef1c quan v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed1i chi\u1ebfu tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp trong c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i chi\u1ec1u Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt cho th\u1ea5y Man Utd c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e2u m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. \u00d4ng \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 \u0111ang t\u1ef1 bi\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u00f2 h\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i Pep Guardiola kh\u00f4ng th\u00e8m ch\u1ea5p n\u1eefa r\u1ed3i th\u00f4i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Brighton 3-2 MU\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brighton 3-2 MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/Thong-so-Brighton-0-2-MU.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 d\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn Brighton vs MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><strong>Video tr\u1eadn Brighton 3-2 MU:<br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279543\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/20/brighton-manutd.mp4&autoplay=false&mute=false&vtype=1&playType=0&_admParamTvc=0;0;0;0&_listsuggest=https://kenh14s.cnnd.vn/Handler/Video/ListVideoXML.ashx?watch=0&postroll=true&replay=true&nonVol=true&volume=0.6&boxVideoID=ifVideo-0&nopre=true&midroll=0.8;20s&urlParent=http://kenh14.vn/truc-tiep-h2-brighton-3-2-man-utd-pogba-ghi-ban-tren-cham-phat-den-20180819142040755.chn\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ket-qua-brighton-vs-mu-1982018-172-194837.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/ket-qua-brighton-vs-mu-1982018.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ket-qua-brighton-vs-mu-1982018-172-194837.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Brighton vs MU tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</span><br>\r\nChuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Brighton vs MU tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 2 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, di\u1ec5n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2548","checkdouble":"194853"},{"date":"06:24 20/08","title":"3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn M.U g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/3-ly-do-khien-mu-guc-nga-truoc-brighton.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ra v\u1ec1 tay tr\u1eafng. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd h\u01a1n khi h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 15/20 CLB \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn M.U tay tr\u1eafng?\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<h2>1. S\u1ef1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Sanchez</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi Brighton \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, CLB Man United \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Alexis Sanchez v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf t\u1edbi s\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Anthony Martial thay v\u00ec Rashford trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a M.U. Tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn n\u00e0y c\u00f3 v\u1ebb kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Martial l\u00e0 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho th\u1ea5y v\u00ec sao anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng trong chuy\u1ebfn t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn MU g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn MU g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Nhung-yeu-to-khien-MU-guc-nga-truoc-Brighton-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>S\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng Sanchez l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn\u00a0</em><i>M.U g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton</i></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng Sanchez, M.U thi\u1ebfu h\u1eb3n m\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn. Ch\u00ednh s\u1ef1 c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester City trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y khi m\u00e0 Martial thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu Sanchez kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tottenham \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a M.U so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>2. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 Bailly \u2013 Lindelof \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Lindelof m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp d\u1eabn t\u1edbi b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf th\u00ec \u1edf c\u00e1c b\u00e0n thua ti\u1ebfp theo, l\u1ed7i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Eric Bailly.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ee9ng c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Duffy. Ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m kh\u00e1 nghi\u1ec7p d\u01b0 c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brighton ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. Qua \u0111\u00f3 n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean th\u00e0nh 3-1 ngay trong 45 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7p 1.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hang thu M.U\" title=\"H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 M.U\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/NINTCHDBPICT000427596080.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 M.U \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3n \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m, HLV Mourinho \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n h\u00ecnh b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 nh\u01b0 Vidic v\u00e0 Ferdinand hay Bruce v\u00e0 Pallister, l\u00fac n\u00e0y nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a M.U \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn. \u0110\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd kh\u00f3 chinh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch sau th\u1eddi Sir Alex.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 m\u01a1 ng\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ee3t l\u00ean b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7y quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a Brighton nh\u01b0 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng ch\u1eb3ng s\u00e1ng h\u01a1n l\u00e0 bao.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf t\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf anh, Anthony Martial kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n khi b\u1ecb h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Montoya theo k\u00e8m qu\u00e1 ch\u1eb7t. Theo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea, trong su\u1ed1t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian h\u01a1n 60 ph\u00fat c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tung ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u00fat nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Martial\" title=\"Martial\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/mourinho-martial-chi-duoc-thi-dau-vi-sanchez-chan-thuong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Martial kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ed1ng Martial, c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh l\u00e0 Rashford hay Lingard c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y khi b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng theo k\u00e8m ch\u1eb7t. C\u00f2n Lukaku d\u00f9 c\u00f3 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y song anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m khi tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa b\u1ecb chia c\u1eaft b\u1edfi l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00ecn chung \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng M.U kh\u00e1 \u2018\u0111\u00f3i b\u00f3ng\u2019 do tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a minh. M\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta l\u1ea1i th\u1ea5y t\u00e2n binh Fred ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi ch\u01b0a ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 thu h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 lu\u00e2n chuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng cho h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. Trong khi nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018, Paul Pogba c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u\u00a0t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n l\u00e0 bao.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 76 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u00e0 2 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng Pogba ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf san b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0nh ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i ra v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2-3 chung cu\u1ed9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f3m l\u1ea1i, th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u1edf c\u1ea3 h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a M.U. V\u00e0 Mourinho c\u1ea7n kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u01a1 t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u trong m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/scholes-noi-ve-that-bai-cua-mu-172-194852.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/scholes-noi-ve-that-bai-cua-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/scholes-noi-ve-that-bai-cua-mu-172-194852.html\">M.U thua tan n\u00e1t, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Scholes n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 M.U thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng y\u1ebfu Brighton & Hove Albion ngay \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Scholes...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-cay-dang-chia-se-ve-tran-thua-tham-o-brighton-172-194849.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/mourinho-cay-dang-chia-se-ve-tran-thua-tham-o-brighton.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-cay-dang-chia-se-ve-tran-thua-tham-o-brighton-172-194849.html\">Mourinho cay \u0111\u1eafng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn thua th\u1ea3m \u1edf Brighton</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Man Utd c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng ra v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi hai b\u00e0n tay tr\u1eafng sau m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 k\u00e9m c\u1ecfi ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cap-trung-ve-mu-bi-bo-doi-huyen-thoai-tong-si-va-sau-tham-bai-o-brighton-172-194848.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/cap-trung-ve-mu-bi-bo-doi-huyen-thoai-tong-si-va-sau-tham-bai-o-brighton.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cap-trung-ve-mu-bi-bo-doi-huyen-thoai-tong-si-va-sau-tham-bai-o-brighton-172-194848.html\">C\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 MU b\u1ecb b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i t\u1ed5ng s\u1ec9 v\u1ea3 sau th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i \u1edf Brighton</span><br>\r\nEric Bailly v\u00e0 Victor Lindelof tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a Gary Neville v\u00e0 Paul Scholes sau tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<em>Highlight: Brighton 2-0 MU (V\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19)<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</em></p>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279543\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/20/brighton-manutd.mp4&autoplay=false&mute=false&vtype=1&playT