hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n Vi\u1ec7t Nam khi l\u1ef1c s\u1ef9 s\u1ed1 1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam,Th\u1ea1ch Kim Tu\u1ea5n b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tranh t\u00e0i h\u1ea1ng c\u00e2n 56kg m\u00f4n c\u1eed t\u1ea1 l\u00fac 17h00. Kim Tu\u1ea5n \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Asiad 2014 \u1edf h\u1ea1ng c\u00e2n n\u00e0y v\u00e0 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u201cn\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m\u201d chi\u1ebfc HCB c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nC\u00f9ng tranh t\u00e0i v\u1edbi Kim Tu\u1ea5n \u1edf n\u1ed9i dung n\u00e0y c\u00f2n c\u00f3 Tr\u1ea7n L\u00ea Qu\u1ed1c To\u00e0n. Ngo\u00e0i h\u1ea1ng c\u00e2n 56kg c\u1ee7a nam, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u1eed t\u1ea1 c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t hy v\u1ecdng \u1edf 2 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Thu\u00fd v\u00e0 V\u01b0\u01a1ng Th\u1ecb Huy\u1ec1n (h\u1ea1ng c\u00e2n 48kg n\u1eef) thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00fac 14h00 c\u00f9ng ng\u00e0y.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra t\u1ea1i m\u00f4n Wushu, \u0111o\u00e0n Vi\u1ec7t Nam hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f4n wushu khi n\u1eef tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Kh\u00e1nh Ly ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tranh n\u1ed9i dung Th\u00e1i c\u1ef1c ki\u1ebfm. Trong l\u00fac Thu\u1ef3 Chi g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u hy v\u1ecdng \u1edf n\u1ed9i dung Nam \u0111ao.<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 208 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n TTVN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 208 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n TTVN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/Lich-thi-dau-Asiad-2018-ngay-hom-nay-208-cua-doan-TTVN-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 208 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n TTVN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 208 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n TTVN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/lichthidauasiad1-thethaoplu.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 208 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n TTVN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 208 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n TTVN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/lichthidauasiad2-thethaoplu.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 ng\u00e0y 20/8 c\u1ee7a TTVN</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br /></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2546","checkdouble":"194859"},{"date":"14:15 19/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Empoli vs Cagliari 23h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (Serie A 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/nhan-dinh-empoli-vs-cagliari-23h00-ngay-198-serie-a-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Empoli vs Cagliari l\u00fac 23h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (V\u00f2ng 1 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Italia Serie A 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Empoli vs Cagliari 23h00 ng\u00e0y 198 Serie A 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Empoli vs Cagliari 23h00 ng\u00e0y 198 Serie A 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/Empoli-vs-Cagliari.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Empoli vs Cagliari</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span>Empoli vs Cagliari: 1-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Ch\u1ec9 sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng ch\u01a1i Serie B, Empoli \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Serie A. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c bu\u00f4ng Coppa Italia \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t: tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 M\u1ef3 \u1ed1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a H\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua, Empoli \u0111\u00e3 chi h\u01a1n 13 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 v\u00e0i t\u00e2n binh, trong \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Antonino La Gumina t\u1eeb Palermo (9 tri\u1ec7u). \u0110\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chia tay v\u00e0i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh b\u1edfi Empoli c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m l\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n Serie A m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Cagliari, Empoli \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n, m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n v\u00ec \u01b0u th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp c\u1eeda tr\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Serie A<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng h\u00f2ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u1ea3 quan trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n+ Trong 12 l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, Empoli c\u00f3 5 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, Cagliari th\u1eafng 4 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 h\u00f2a nhau 3 l\u1ea7n<br>\r\n+ Cagliari ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1/6 tr\u1eadn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Empoli v\u00e0 thua c\u1ea3 5 tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2545","checkdouble":"194811"},{"date":"14:59 19/08","title":"\"Pogba v\u00e0 Mourinho c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/pogba-va-mourinho-can-phai-truong-thanh-hon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Paul Ince cho r\u1eb1ng Mourinho v\u00e0 Pogba c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n v\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 thay v\u00ec ch\u00fa \u00fd nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 \u1edf s\u00e2n Old Trafford l\u00e0 Mourinho v\u00e0 Pogba li\u00ean t\u1ee5c xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean c\u00e1c m\u1eb7t b\u00e1o g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y v\u00ec tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi nhau. Mourinho c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ch\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n n\u00e0y v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 vui m\u1eebng h\u01a1n v\u1edbi c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00f3 v\u1ebb c\u0169ng kh\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng khi Pogba kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng anh s\u1ebd gi\u1ea5u k\u00edn m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paul Ince Pogba v\u00e0 Mourinho c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Paul Ince Pogba v\u00e0 Mourinho c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/pogba-va-mourinho-can-phai-truong-thanh-hon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Paul Ince cho r\u1eb1ng Pogba v\u00e0 Mourinho c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Paul Ince cho r\u1eb1ng Mourinho v\u00e0 Pogba n\u00ean g\u1ea1t b\u1ecf nh\u1eefng m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f9ng nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t h\u01b0\u1edbng. Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean k\u00eanh BBC v\u1ec1 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn trong n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 MU, \u00f4ng cho bi\u1ebft:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cTr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ebft, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Pogba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng. Ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi nhau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cPogba \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Mourinho c\u0169ng trao b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng cho Pogba. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y \u00f4ng \u1ea5y t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ra sao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cPogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt. Nh\u01b0ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Pogba l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n v\u00e0 l\u1ea1i kh\u01a1i d\u1eady tr\u00ed t\u00f2 m\u00f2 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1nh ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. Tranh c\u00e3i n\u00e0y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd c\u00f2n k\u00e9o d\u00e0i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta n\u00ean n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Man United l\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn xa t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng Mourinho hay Pogba. H\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i l\u00f9i v\u1ec1 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-brighton-vs-man-utd-22h00-ngay-198-cau-tra-loi-tren-san-co-172-194787.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brighton vs Man Utd (22h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8): C\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nhan-mot-loat-tin-vui-truoc-tran-gap-brighton-172-194765.html\">M.U nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t tin vui tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Brighton</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2544","checkdouble":"194812"},{"date":"14:38 19/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nimes vs Marseille 02h00 ng\u00e0y 20/8 (Ligue 1 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/nhan-dinh-nimes-vs-marseille-02h00-ngay-208-ligue-1-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs N\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs N\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan b\u1ea3ng C m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef Asiad 2018 l\u00fac 18h30 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 19/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00e1c v\u1edbi hai b\u1ea3ng A v\u00e0 B, b\u1ea3ng C c\u1ee7a m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef ASIAD 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 thay v\u00ec 4 \u0111\u1ed9i tranh t\u00e0i. V\u00e0 2 \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ebd \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00e1 th\u0103m may r\u1ee7i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o \u0111\u00fang b\u1ea3ng C c\u00f9ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan. M\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eb1m trong tay c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n x\u1ee9 hoa anh \u0111\u00e0o. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs N\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs N\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/20180816_100127.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs N\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7n n\u00f3i th\u00eam l\u00e0 3 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra, Th\u00e1i Lan ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ecbu thua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 0-2. Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n th\u1ebf, t\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 thua v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng C sau \u0111\u00e2y 2 ng\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ec3 ganh \u0111ua v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 v\u1edbi Th\u00e1i Lan. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, ngay c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u00f4 g\u00e1i x\u1ee9 ch\u00f9a V\u00e0ng chi\u1ec1u nay c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c ki\u1ebfm v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nDo \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ec7nh l\u1ec7nh ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung \u0111\u01b0a ra cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2. \u201cG\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. N\u1ebfu th\u1eafng, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong c\u1ee7a \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 99%. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y\u201d, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n l\u00e3o luy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7t Nam: H\u1ea3i Y\u1ebfn; Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng Th\u1ecb Ki\u1ec1u, H\u1ed3ng Nhung, Ph\u1ea1m Th\u1ecb T\u01b0\u01a1i, Th\u00f9y Dung; Tuy\u1ebft Dung, Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Li\u1ec5u, Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb V\u1ea1n, M\u1ef9 Anh; Hu\u1ef3nh Nh\u01b0, H\u1ea3i Y\u1ebfn. <br>\r\nTh\u00e1i Lan: Nattaruja; Warunee, Sunisan, Natthakarn, Kanjanaporn; Kanjana, Rattikan, Orathai, Pikul, Silawan; Taneekarn.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2543","checkdouble":"194813"},{"date":"14:31 19/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Strasbourg vs St.Etienne 20h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (Ligue 1 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/nhan-dinh-strasbourg-vs-stetienne-20h00-ngay-198-ligue-1-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Strasbourg vs St.Etienne l\u00fac 20h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (V\u00f2ng 2 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Ph\u00e1p Ligue 1 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Strasbourg vs StEtienne 20h ng\u00e0y 198 Ligue 1 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Strasbourg vs StEtie