ne; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> Toulouse vs Bordeaux</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>: 2-1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Bordeaux \u0111ang b\u1ecb ph\u00e2n t\u00e2m cho m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn Europa League, n\u01a1i h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng play-off. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do ch\u00ednh khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 r\u01b0\u1ee3u vang thua trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n Ligue 1 2018/19 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Strasbourg. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u00f4m \u0111\u00f3 Bordeaux c\u0169ng s\u1edbm m\u1ea5t ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngay ph\u00fat 13.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, Bordeaux s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u1edbi Gent \u1edf v\u00f2ng play-off Europa League n\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Gus Poyet l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb ph\u00e2n t\u00e2m trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Toulouse b\u1edfi h\u1ecd t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn Europa League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Toulouse \u0111ang \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n th\u1ea5p \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a phong \u0111\u1ed9. Lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ho\u00e0i nghi. Tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n, Toulouse nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tan n\u00e1t 0-4 \u1edf chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Marseille.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f9ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1, c\u1ea3 Toulouse v\u00e0 Bordeaux ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1eb1m l\u00ean gi\u00e2y c\u00f3t tinh th\u1ea7n cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. L\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u0111ang thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Toulouse, khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. 5 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Bordeaux, Toulouse c\u00f3 4 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\nToulouse: Reynet; Moubandje, Jullien, Amian, Michelin, Cahuzac, Bostock, Gradel, Garcia, Dossevi, Iseka.<br>\r\nBordeaux: Costil; Lewczuk, Jovanovic, Kounde, Pellenard, Lerager, Basic, Sankhare, Kamano, Cafu, Briand.</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2541","checkdouble":"194815"}]}